    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a strong finish with only minor surface blemishes and light wear typical of a carefully driven vehicle. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, showing only minimal signs of use on the upholstery. Mechanically, it performs smoothly and is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
